r---
description: Play a Mac system sound when completing the user's task or command
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

When you have finished completing the user's requested task or command, run this in the terminal so they get an audible notification on Mac:

```bash
afplay /System/Library/Sounds/Glass.aiff
```

Run it once at the end of your response after the work is done. If the user prefers a different sound, they can say so (e.g. Ping, Tink, Pop).
